---
title: Cheesy Pesto Orzotto with Heirloom Tomatoes and Yellow Squash
description: Pasta night just got a whole lot more interesting (and delicious!). Cooking orzo risotto-style means minimal effort (see: less stirring, one pan, easy clean-up) and maximal flavor. This orzotto is loaded with tender spring veggies and a swirl of herbaceous pesto. Lemon juice adds a bright note and chili flakes lend a touch of heat. Plus: there’s cheese--two kinds!! This spring-inspired dish is sure to put a pep in your step.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w23-r8-cheesy-pesto-orzotto-6c522f68.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w23-r8-cheesy-pesto-orzotto-5cc202d9efe3e4001767ee06-bcecab85.pdf
